  {
    "row": 144,
    "rowsha": "Y7/WGgVhslWiyqCi463Qkcp+Mn8voGpAfLsv80G4WNg=",
    "originContent": "## Usage",
    "translatedContent": "## 使い方"
  },
  {
    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "Kckjf5IxqYIlXCyJRdkyIcvUSAugIhCyYXz70/2tiVw=",
    "originContent": "To obfuscate your resources and generate an obfuscated AAB, run the following Gradle command in the project's root",
    "translatedContent": "リソースを難読化し、難読化されたAABを生成するには、プロジェクトのルートディレクトリで以下のGradleコマンドを実行してください。:"
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "sCcWvl6kSXzA7wJGRMtx4Q5O9CNZtTHf2iRTg1+xfJo=",
    "originContent": "directory.:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 148,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 149,
    "rowsha": "OdQQfokK9VAr+KbNi/Vu3u/NAu1JNDE4jS0EyS2AGb4=",
    "originContent": "```cmd",
    "translatedContent": "```cmd"
  },
  {
    "row": 150,
    "rowsha": "/R5sbNTF1mdrZjRJ1cxf4H8NQjNAq2+8Z2RpKpN0ego=",
    "originContent": "./gradle clean :app:resChiperDebug --stacktrace",
    "translatedContent": "./gradle clean :app:resChiperDebug --stacktrace"
  },
  {
    "row": 151,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 152,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "このコマンドはプロジェクトのルートから難読化プロセスを実行し、難読化されたAABは"
  },
  {
    "row": 153,
    "rowsha": "qQUKDK3OwVty9L+CjzacZUcE//JOcRzj1t/1qCBWNGA=",
    "originContent": "This command will execute the obfuscation process from the project root, and the obfuscated AAB will be generated in",
    "translatedContent": "`app/build/outputs/bundle/debug` ディレクトリに生成されます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 154,
    "rowsha": "6x1iB0RYvL9px0b7MWKNuEsN3Y+x4I2kNpP3DMG5reI=",
    "originContent": "the `app/build/outputs/bundle/debug` directory.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 155,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 設定オプション"
  },
  {
    "row": 156,
    "rowsha": "V9KSt2YGHWHKhLFXw8vhKEfBj8HIXJIPsF8Xv1NwUTI=",
    "originContent": "## Configuration Options",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 157,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "ResChiper拡張機能は、リソース難読化のための様々な設定オプションを提供しており、難読化の有効/無効、"
  },
  {
    "row": 158,
    "rowsha": "R302s4VgdQsxZwH/7XCKlXqERQbFw7TDyPfUw+2n8mc=",
    "originContent": "The ResChiper extension provides various configuration options for resource obfuscation, including enabling/disabling",
    "translatedContent": "マッピングファイルの指定、リソースのホワイトリスト設定などが含まれます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 159,
    "rowsha": "uIehel6OVQ4o3X4N7bOb3H7vMlt9nVbhKqybeht7i0g=",
    "originContent": "obfuscation, specifying mapping files, white-listing resources, and more.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 160,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- `enableObfuscation`: リソース難読化の有効化または無効化。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 161,
    "rowsha": "lTXQA/tM58thvkYaQJ29nQKIlZZz6kPZrFLNA2dpWdM=",
    "originContent": "- `enableObfuscation`: Enable or disable resource obfuscation.<br>",
    "translatedContent": "- `obfuscationMode`: ディレクトリのみを難読化する場合は `obfuscationMode = \"dir\"`、ファイルのみを難読化する場合は"
  },
  {
    "row": 162,
    "rowsha": "14ZoPmmpiRbQTDlIUBr4KA8JM06H89rrGrH6RyTLlMA=",
    "originContent": "- `obfuscationMode`: to obfuscate only directories set `obfuscationMode = \"dir\"`, to obfuscate only files set",
    "translatedContent": "  `obfuscationMode = \"file\"`、ディレクトリとファイルの両方を難読化する場合は `obfuscationMode = \"default\"` を設定します。<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "ryFMCW+/+ohlREMMmaV8go5Tea4xHF4kUoDKMcNa0Sk=",
    "originContent": "  `obfuscationMode = \"file\"` and to obfuscate both directory and files set `obfuscationMode = \"default\"`.<br>",
